{
  "title": "Heat storage depends on specific heat",
  "publicationStatus": "public",
  "subtitle": "Why do some materials take longer to heat up or cool down than others?",
  "about": [
    "How much heat is stored in an object depends on its specific heat, as described by the formula below:",
    "",
    "*Q* = **c**p · **m**(*T*final-*T*initial)",
    "",
    "Note: The specific heats of the two objects are different.",
    "",
    "Run the model and note the temperatures measured by the two thermometers.",
    "Adjust the heat capacity of each block with the sliders. Can you predict the final temperature?"
  ],
  "importedFrom": "imports/energy2d/content-htb/S1B.html",
  "models": [
    {
      "type": "energy2d",
      "id": "S1B1",
      "url": "models-converted/lab-version/1/energy2d/S1B1.json",
      "importedFrom": "imports/energy2d/models-xml/S1B1.e2d",
      "viewOptions": {
        "controlButtons": "play_reset"
      }
    }
  ],
  "parameters": [
    {
      "name": "left-block",
      "label": "Left block specific heat",
      "unitAbbreviation": "kg · °C",
      "onChange": "getPart(0).specific_heat = value;",
      "initialValue": 1000
    },
    {
      "name": "right-block",
      "label": "Right block specific heat",
      "unitAbbreviation": "kg · °C",
      "onChange": "getPart(1).specific_heat = value;",
      "initialValue": 2000
    }
  ],
  "components": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "specific-heat-label",
      "text": "### Specific heat (kg · °C):"
    },
    {
      "type": "slider",
      "id": "left-block-slider",
      "property": "left-block",
      "title": "Left block",
      "min": 100,
      "max": 5000,
      "displayValue": "return format('.1f')(value)",
      "labels": [
        {
          "value": 100,
          "label": "100"
        },
        {
          "value": 5000,
          "label": "5000"
        }
      ],
      "steps": 49,
      "width": "10em"
    },
    {
      "type": "slider",
      "id": "right-block-slider",
      "property": "right-block",
      "title": "Right block",
      "min": 100,
      "max": 5000,
      "displayValue": "return format('.1f')(value)",
      "labels": [
        {
          "value": 100,
          "label": "100"
        },
        {
          "value": 5000,
          "label": "5000"
        }
      ],
      "steps": 49,
      "width": "10em"
    },
    {
      "type": "graph",
      "id": "graph",
      "title": "Temperature Probes: T1, T2",
      "xlabel": "Time (s)",
      "ylabel": "Temperature (°C)",
      "ymin": 0,
      "ymax": 50,
      "xmax": 300,
      "xTickCount": 5,
      "xFormatter": ".2s",
      "yFormatter": ".2s",
      "xProperty": "time",
      "properties": [
        "sensor-0", "sensor-1"
      ],
      "legendLabels": [
      "T1",
      "T2"
      ],
      "legendVisible": true
    }
  ],
  "layout": {
    "bottom": [
      "specific-heat-label", "left-block-slider", "right-block-slider"
    ],
    "right": [ "graph" ]
  },
  "template": "wide-right"
}
